=Wahl|first1=Grant|title=Charlie Stillitano Decides Against Running for U.S. Soccer President|url=https://www.si.com/soccer/2017/10/24/charlie-stillitano-us-soccer-president-election-sunil-gulati|website=Sports Illustrated|publisher=Time Inc.|accessdate=October 24, 2017|date=October 24, 2017}}</ref>\n\n== Endorsements ==\n{{Endorsements box\n| title = Eric Wynalda\n| list = \n;Leagues\n*[[National Premier Soccer League]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.npsl.com/news_article/show/872513?referrer_id=1510764|title=Statement From The NPSL|website=npsl.com|accessdate=January 5, 2018}}</ref>\n*[[National Independent Soccer Association]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nisaofficial.com/2017/12/21/nisa-endorses-eric-wynalda-for-ussf-president/|title=NISA Endorses Eric Wynalda for USSF President - NISA|website=Nisaofficial.com|accessdate=7 January 2018}}</ref>\n*[[North American Soccer League]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nasl.com/news/2018/01/17/-north-american-soccer-league-announces-support-for-eric-wynalda-in-upcoming-united-states-soccer-federation-presidential-election|title=NASL Announces Support For Eric Wynalda In Upcoming USSF Presidential Election\n|accessdate=20 January 2018}}</ref>\n*NorCal Premier Soccer<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/NorCalPreSoccer/status/951581205132058624|title=NorCal Premier Soccer is excited to endorse @EricWynalda for US Soccer President and has released the following statement on the matter. |date=January 11, 2018}}</ref>\n;Organizations\n*Rush Soccer<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rushsoccer.com/Default.aspx?tabid=1191480&mid=1281647&newskeyid=HN1&newsid=80041457&ctl=newsdetail|title=Home|website=Rushsoccer.com|accessdate=7 January 2018}}</ref>\n*American Soccer United<ref>{{cite web|url=http://americansoccerunited.com/2018-us-soccer-presidential-election/|title=2018 US Soccer Presidential Election - American Soccer United|website=Americansoccerunited.com|accessdate=7 January 2018}}</ref>\n;Soccer Associations\n*New Hampshire Socc